I am not sure if there even is an uncut version. HBO is a private cable network, you have to subscribe to and pay, if you want to watch their program. They are not restricted by public moral standards, like the public networks (NBC,CBS,ABC,etc.) So they pretty much can show whatever they like.
However this torrent consists of the TVRips ripped from HBO. So probably (at least within standards of other countries that may air this series on public networks) this is uncut.

